WEBVTT

00:03:27.861 --> 00:03:31.926
Besh yil Yaponiyada yashab, 
hunarimni rivojlantirganimdan keyin,

00:03:31.950 --> 00:03:34.400
Menga endi yangi cho'qqilar kerak edi,

00:03:34.903 --> 00:03:36.110
Keyin Nyu-Yorkka ketdim,

00:03:36.134 --> 00:03:38.379
chunki rassom sifatida
shunday qilish kerak edi,

00:03:38.403 --> 00:03:40.394
Dunyoning eng zo'r shahriga ko'chish,

00:03:40.418 --> 00:03:41.642
shunga imkon berardiki

00:03:41.666 --> 00:03:45.873
siz o'zingizni butunlay
ko'rinmasdek his qilasiz.

00:03:46.788 --> 00:03:49.882
Mana shu payt men o'zimdan
so'ray boshladim,

00:03:49.906 --> 00:03:52.255
"Sen kimsan o'zi?"

00:03:52.279 --> 00:03:55.288
Tongda uyg'onib, 
kunimni boshlashdan oldin,

00:03:55.312 --> 00:03:57.006
Shu haqida chuqur o'ylardim.

00:03:57.030 --> 00:03:58.991
Shu hayol bilan

00:03:59.015 --> 00:04:00.498
chizishni davom ettirdim.